    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "41bfd2c8_ca0dab1e",
        "filename": "luci_notify/notify/srcman.go",
        "patchSetId": 12
      },
      "lineNbr": 135,
      "author": {
        "id": 1114299
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-06-04T15:51:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "note that populateHistory and this func deal only with git-aspect of source manifest. This is a sign that we are at a wrong level of abstraction.\n\nbuildbucket api won\u0027t expose source manifests, so most of our code should not deal with them directly. We should only fetch them to retrieve commits (because buildbucket doesn\u0027t do so yet) and that code will be deleted as soon as buildbucket provides output commits.\n\nIf we accept two maps (repo -\u003e revision) for old and new build, then we can use history func to compute the blamelist, i.e. collapse populateHistory and this func into one. This will simplify this code because map[string]string and gitiles-level abstractions are simpler than source manifest.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 135,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 135,
        "endChar": 22
      },
      "revId": "0ae4858bf1590fda9d98044e39261ac37cc57232",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "b0efdbf2_886590fb",
        "filename": "luci_notify/notify/srcman.go",
        "patchSetId": 12
      },
      "lineNbr": 135,
      "author": {
        "id": 1154295
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-06-05T21:02:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "good call; I was under the assumption that source manifests would be the lingua franca for this sort of stuff, but if it\u0027s not (and we\u0027re not actually dealing with them regularly once buildbucket supports gitiles_commits) then it totally makes sense not to use them as the data structure to carry all this information. it is indeed more complex. my notion was that one day perhaps one could trace even CIPD prebuilts toward a blamelist, but that\u0027s a lot more future work.",
      "parentUuid": "41bfd2c8_ca0dab1e",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 135,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 135,
        "endChar": 22
      },
      "revId": "0ae4858bf1590fda9d98044e39261ac37cc57232",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
